"title": "1462: truth, in NT",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1462",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The NT encompasses the Greek idea of truth as reality, as well as the Hebraic concepts of faithfulness and reliability. Jesus Christ is shown as “the Truth” and the apostles present the gospel as “truth”.</p>\n<h2>Truth as opposed to falsehood and lies</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:25\">EPH 4:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:33\">JHN 3:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:37\">JHN 4:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:23\">JHN 18:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:35\">JHN 19:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:1\">ACT 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:24\">ACT 21:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:8\">ACT 24:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:25\">ACT 26:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18\">ROM 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:1\">ROM 9:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:54\">1CO 15:54</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:14\">2CO 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:16\">GAL 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:13\">TIT 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:22\">2PE 2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:4\">1JN 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:1-2John1:2\">2JN 1:1–1:2</a></p>\n<h2>Truth as reality</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:24\">HEB 9:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:9\">JHN 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:23\">JHN 4:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:3\">JHN 17:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:24\">EPH 4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:9\">1TH 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:2\">1TI 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:19\">1TI 6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:2\">TIT 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:2\">TIT 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:2\">HEB 8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:8\">HEB 12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:12\">1PE 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:5\">1JN 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:8\">1JN 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:9\">REV 19:9</a></p>\n<h3>Truth as trustworthy affirmations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:47\">JHN 6:47</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:2\">MAT 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:23\">MAT 10:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:28\">MAT 16:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:23\">MAT 19:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:36\">MAT 23:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:13\">MAT 26:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:41\">MRK 9:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:23\">MRK 11:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:44\">LUK 12:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:3\">LUK 21:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:51\">JHN 1:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24-John5:25\">JHN 5:24–5:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:34\">JHN 8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:7\">JHN 10:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:7\">JHN 16:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:15\">PHP 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:9\">1TI 3:9</a></p>\n<h2>Truth as faithfulness and reliability</h2>\n<h3>The quality of truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:8\">PHP 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:17\">JHN 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:21\">JHN 3:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:24\">JHN 4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:17\">JHN 17:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:20\">ROM 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:8\">1CO 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:6\">1CO 13:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:8\">2CO 13:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:9\">EPH 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:14\">EPH 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:12\">3JN 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>Truth as an aspect of the character of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:3-Rom3:4\">ROM 3:3–3:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:4\">PSA 51:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:7\">ROM 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:8\">ROM 15:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:7\">REV 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:14\">REV 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:10\">REV 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:3\">REV 15:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:7\">REV 16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:2\">REV 19:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:11\">REV 19:11</a></p>\n<h3>Truth as a human quality</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:23\">ACT 11:23</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:8\">1JN 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:21\">JHN 3:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:18\">JHN 7:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:22\">ACT 14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:15\">EPH 4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:18\">PHP 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:13\">REV 2:13</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ as truth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6\">JHN 14:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:1\">JHN 15:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:37-John18:38\">JHN 18:37–18:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a></p>\n<h2>The Spirit of God as truth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16-John14:17\">JHN 14:16–14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:6\">1JN 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:6\">1JN 5:6</a></p>\n<h2>The gospel and the Christian faith as truth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13\">EPH 1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:31-John8:32\">JHN 8:31–8:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:30\">ACT 20:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:2\">2CO 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:5\">GAL 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:5\">COL 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:3-1Tim2:4\">1TI 2:3–2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:6\">1TI 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:18\">2TI 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:4\">2TI 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:1\">TIT 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:19\">JAS 5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:2\">2PE 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:19\">1JN 3:19</a></p>",
